---
title: Loaded Meatless Burger with Spiced Potato Wedges
description: A cascade of restaurant-worthy toppings awaits with tonight's Meatless Farm burger. Spiced crisped potato wedges and spiked ketchup are the perfect side companions!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/vegeburgers-tout-garnis-b328523b.jpg
